Package: InterSpatial
Type: Package
Title: Inter-Modality Cell Communication via Spatial and scRNA-seq Integration
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Tuhin", "Majumder", email = "majumdertuhin96@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for integrative analysis of spatial transcriptomics and scRNA-seq data. Includes SCTransform normalization, intermodality probability matrix computation, hierarchical clustering using ClusteringTree, and Wasserstein distance calculation for cluster comparison. Parallelization supported.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
